## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Prerequisites:
- Node.js & npm
- MongoDB
- Cloudinary account (for image uploads)

### Run Locally

1. Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/estategrid.git
````

2. Setup server

```bash
cd estategrid/server
npm install
npm run dev
```

3. Setup client

```bash
cd estategrid/client
npm install
npm start
```

